query: ALTER TABLE container_registry_manifest_blob ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_manifest_blob_pk PRIMARY KEY(manifest_digest, blob_digest), ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_manifest_blob_fk_manifest_digest FOREIGN KEY(manifest_digest) REFERENCES container_registry_manifest(manifest_digest), ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_manifest_blob_fk_blob_digest FOREIGN KEY(blob_digest) REFERENCES container_registry_repository_blob(blob_digest), ADD CONSTRAINT container_registry_manifest_blob_fk_parent_blob_digest FOREIGN KEY(parent_blob_digest) REFERENCES container_registry_repository_blob(blob_digest);
